<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>UnFumble App — Coming Soon</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: #050a0e;
        color: #e2e8f0;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        background: rgba(20,184,166,0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);
        color: #5eead4;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14b8a6, #818cf8);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      p { color: #64748b; max-width: 30ch; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6; }
      a {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        background: rgba(20,184,166,0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);
        color: #5eead4;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      a:hover { background: rgba(20,184,166,0.2); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <div class="badge">🚧 In progress</div>
      <h1>App coming soon</h1>
      <p>The UnFumble AI engine is being wired up. Check back soon.</p>
      <a href="/">← Back to landing page</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
